tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE QuantumErrorCorrectionResults (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_name TEXT,
    error_correction_technique TEXT,
    error_rate FLOAT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE QuantumResults (
  result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  error_id INT,
  code_id INT,
  result_data TEXT,
  FOREIGN KEY (error_id) REFERENCES QuantumErrors(error_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (code_id) REFERENCES QuantumCodes(code_id)
);

CREATE TABLE error_logs (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  error_id INT,
  qubit_id INT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  foreign key (error_id) references quantum_error_correction(error_id),
  foreign key (qubit_id) references qubits(qubit_id)
);
